  "intro": "<p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: windowtext; letter-spacing: 0pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">炎炎烈日，酷暑高温，盛夏时节，每个焦躁繁杂的生命，都渴望一丝清凉，“清凉水，清水一渠，涤荡诸污秽”。让我们的内心生出清凉之水，溶化一切怨恨和矛盾，清心、倾心。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: windowtext; letter-spacing: 0pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">桑吉平措2016盛夏高温时节，再度送来《清凉歌》，歌词选自一代善德——李叔同先生。那片意境，那一份爱，足以让你我清凉身心，消暑解愠。</span></p>\n <p></p>",
